channel.title: [421] Changing some stuff
channel.description:
I am very bored, well, actually i have to clean up my room, but anyways im bored :P. [i] Notes:[/i] [tt])1 is , )2 is - )3 is . )4 is / (W is ' (V is & Please post more if you find them.[/tt]
Here are some VERY basic stuff to change:
[u]Runescape is loading, please wait...[/u] Open up Class47 and search for [code]RuneScape is loading[/code] You will find this: (unless your deob is fucked) [code] .method479("RuneScape is loading )2 please wait)3)3)3", 255);[/code] Just change [tt]RuneScape is loading )2 please wait)3)3)3[/tt] to whatever you want.
[u]Welcome to RuneScape[/u] Open Class65 and search for [code]Welcome to RuneScape[/code] You will find this: [code] = Class39_Sub5_Sub8.method479("Welcome to RuneScape", 255);[/code] Change [tt]Welcome to RuneScape[/tt] to whatever you want.
[u]Making Credits (New User)[/u] First, open Class61 and search for [code]New User[/code] You will then find this: [code] aClass50_1422 = Class39_Sub5_Sub8.method479("New User", 255);[/code] Edit [code]New User[/code] to [tt]Credits[/tt] (or whatever you want to do). Then open Class40 and search for [code]Create a free account[/code] If you've done it right, you'll find this: [code] = Class39_Sub5_Sub8.method479("Create a free account", 255);[/code] Change [tt]Create a free account[/tt] to [tt]My Client Credits[/tt] (or whatever). Now open Class7 and search for [tt]To create a[/tt] and you'll find this: [code] .method479("To create a new account you need to", 255);[/code] Change [tt]To create a new account you need to[/tt] to [tt]Thisbot is created by Myname.[/tt] Then open Class3 and search for [tt]Go back to the[/tt] and you'll find this: [tt] = Class39_Sub5_Sub8.method479("go back to the main RuneScape webpage",[/tt] Change [tt]go back to the main RuneScape webpage[/tt] to [tt]Website: www.mywebsite.com[/tt]. Now open Class35 and search for [tt]and choose the[/tt]. You will find: [code] = Class39_Sub5_Sub8.method479("and choose the (Wcreate account(W",[/code] Change [tt]and choose the (Wcreate account(W[/tt] to [tt](c) Copyright MyCompany. Then you will have to open Class33 and search for [tt]button near the top[/tt] and you will find this stuff: [code] = Class39_Sub5_Sub8.method479("button near the top of that page)3",[/code] Change [tt]button near the top of that page)3[/tt] to [tt]All Rights Reserved[/tt].
[u]Existing User[/u] Open Class39 and search for [tt]Existing user[/tt]. You will find this: [code] aClass50_948 = Class39_Sub5_Sub8.method479("Existing user", 255);[/code] Change [tt]Existing user[/tt] to [tt]Start the Game[/tt] or whatever. Then open Class39_Sub5_Sub11_Sub3_Sub2 and search for [tt]Enter your username[/tt]. What you find is the following: [code] = Class39_Sub5_Sub8.method479("Enter your username (V password)3",[/code] Change [tt]Enter your username (V password)3[/tt] to, well, whatever. Open Class64 and search for Login, you'll find: [code] aClass50_1466 = Class39_Sub5_Sub8.method479("Login", 255);[/code] Change [tt]Login[/tt] to Start RS or something.
Now im sooo bored, so check out the rest yourself.
- Pimjong
